                                Sextus</title> (1959). (with Greek and Latin texts)</bibl>
                        <bibl>P.  de  Lagarde, <title rend="italic">Analecta Syriaca</title> (1858,
                            <abbr>repr.</abbr> 1967), iii–xi (collations), 2–31 (text).</bibl>
